{"tid":942251,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"(橫豎撇點勾) 小弟手寫二萬字 寫成一幅畫","createTime":"2018-12-15T14:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T18:24:27.000Z","uid":143257,"like":1427,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe2fec0c76f87ef615276feb7931b81f484c99a","tid":942251,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"小弟好耐之前開post講過 樹葉 兩毫 砌畫<br />\n今次就開過post係關於[ 繁體中文字 ]既創作<br />\n係post圖之前，其實我想講講點解我會選擇呢三種東西作為創作媒介<br />\n簡單黎講，樹葉/兩毫/繁體中文字 都係一啲因社會進步，而逐漸消失或遺忘既野<br />\n繁體中文字 ，依加多數人溝通方式都係語音或電子媒介打字，書寫文化越黎越少。<br />\n其次，繁體中文字係香港文化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w40oeav9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw40oeav9&h=848a08f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yrcidgqn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyrcidgqn&h=5c3c238f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩個係粵劇 小生同花旦，當中文字內容係用段落形式描述粵劇。<br />\n大概19,000字<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ou0m2ank\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fou0m2ank&h=74048ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅文字內容係描述李小龍既身平，電影作品及哲學金句。<br />\n呢幅作品大概22,000字<br />\n<br />\n黎緊新作品有更多新嘗試<br />\n如果大家中意同想睇多d 不如follow 我art.ig 同facebook page<br />\n當支持下小弟<br />\nig : gllh_art (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=5jwT8us7VeZLNEszoRZoOf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3ddd5b42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a>)<br />\nfb page : Giraffe leung lok hei (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgiraffellh%2F&d=5jwT8us7VeZLNEszoRZoOf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=acae6d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/giraffellh/</a>)"},{"pid":"39d5d12f41e234272905d776653bb2da92494348","tid":942251,"uid":203417,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,